范霍文选中艾恩塞德扮演科海根亲信瑞克特，后者曾参与《机器战警》主角试镜，导演请他出演大反派克拉伦斯·博迪克，但艾恩塞德演过《[[反攻美国|反攻美国]]》（1987年）后不想再演“精神变态”。艾恩塞德认为瑞克特更倾向“反社会人格”，有觊觎科海根地位的个人野心。<ref name="DOGCast" /><ref name="Murray" />{{rp|54}}<ref name="Murray0" />{{rp|59}}谢绝出演《机器战警》和另一部电影导致很多人以为艾恩塞特工作上难以相处，他是在完成试镜后入选。试镜时他扮演的人物精神崩溃倒地痛哭，范霍文拉近拍摄特写。<ref name="DOGCast" /><ref name="BFIORal">{{cite web | first = Josh | last = Slater-Williams | title = I can remember it for you wholesale: The making of Total Recall, 30 years on | url = https://www.bfi.org.uk/interviews/total-recall-paul-verhoeven-michael-ironside | website = British Film Institute | date = 2020-11-24 | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172429/https://www.bfi.org.uk/interviews/total-recall-paul-verhoeven-michael-ironside}}</ref>施瓦辛格认为艾恩塞特体型壮硕，看起来确能对男主角构成威胁<ref name="Murray" />{{rp|54}}。

片中两名女主角对体力要求很高，崇尚运动的蒂科汀和斯通入选<ref name="Murray" />{{rp|52}}。斯通自称健硕体型和生人勿近的为人导致演职人员都把她当男人对待，只有艾恩塞德“一直记得我是女人，拉摔倒的我起身”<ref name="PeopleSchwarzJune52020">{{cite web | first = Benjamin | last = VanHoose | title = Arnold Schwarzenegger Suffered a 'Deep' Wrist Wound While Shooting ''Total Recall'' 30 Years Ago | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | url = https://people.com/movies/arnold-schwarzenegger-says-he-suffered-deep-wrist-wound-while-shooting-total-recall-30-years-ago/ | website = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | date = 2020-06-05 | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172428/https://people.com/movies/arnold-schwarzenegger-says-he-suffered-deep-wrist-wound-while-shooting-total-recall-30-years-ago/ | dead-url = no}}</ref>。范霍文之女为班尼选角，选中约翰逊的试镜带。约翰逊记得是在刚拍完[[黑人剝削電影|黑人剝削電影]]后看到《全面回忆》剧本，看到班尼是“黑人牛仔舞迷”后就把剧本一扔。但他后来看完剧本后还是决定试镜，认为班尼人物塑造很完整，冷酷且精于算计的形象引人入胜。<ref name="SyFyCast2" /><ref name="SyFyat30" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Sue | last =  Martin | title = Mel Johnson Jr. Happy to Be in 'Total Recall' s' Driver's Seat | website = Los Angeles Times| date = 1990-07-28 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-07-28-ca-462-story.html | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172431/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-07-28-ca-462-story.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

考克斯曾与导演在《机器战警》合作，此前长期出演好好先生，与该片大反派对比鲜明。他自称不采用[[方法演技|方法演技]]，而是设身处地地感受人物所思所想，进而决定如何演出。拍摄《全面回忆》时他头发后梳，方便制作特效所需面部模型。考克斯对人物形象很有把握，说服范霍文花两天重拍戏码。<ref name="SyFyat30" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Adam | last = Pockross | title = Ronny Cox Only Played 'Boy Scout Nice-guys' Until Paul Verhoeven Turned Him Bad | url = https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/ronny-cox-total-recall-interview-cohaagen | website = Syfy Wire | date =  2020-06-19 | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516173931/https://www.syfy.com/syfy-wire/ronny-cox-total-recall-interview-cohaagen | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>贝尔试镜时剧本尚未写明乔治和寡头的关系，他还对乔治的台词这么少感到奇怪。剧组本考虑为寡头找配音，导演最后决定直接用贝尔的声音。<ref name="CBRCast" />范霍文根据[[保羅·紐曼|保羅·紐曼]]在[[亞弗列·希治閣|亞弗列·希治閣]]1966年惊悚片《[[冲破铁幕|冲破铁幕]]》扮演的科学家设计艾吉马大夫，希望人物看起来“天真、疏远的同时又有些古怪”，最后选中布罗克斯史密斯<ref>{{cite web | first = Kate| last = Erbland | title = 24 Things We Learned from Paul Verhoeven's 'Total Recall' Commentary | url = https://filmschoolrejects.com/24-things-we-learned-from-the-total-recall-commentary-9e99444bacb2/ | website = [[Film_School_Rejects|Film School Rejects]] | date = 2012-04-19 | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172429/https://filmschoolrejects.com/24-things-we-learned-from-the-total-recall-commentary-9e99444bacb2/ | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制与后期制作 ===
