《全面回忆》1989年4至5日开始[[主体拍摄|主体拍摄]]<ref>{{cite web | first = David | last = Pecchia| title = Films now going into production: ... | website = Los Angeles Times| date = 1989-03-26 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-03-26-ca-930-story.html | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172429/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1989-03-26-ca-930-story.html}}</ref><ref name="Vest" />{{rp|48}}，共持续20周，几乎完全按时间顺序摄制，可谓影史罕见{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="SyFyCast2" /><ref name="SyFyat30" /><ref name="LATimesSchwarz" /><ref name="GizmodoStunt">{{cite web | first = Vic| last = Armstrong | title =  What was it like being a stunt director on Total Recall? | url = https://gizmodo.com/what-was-it-like-being-a-stunt-director-on-total-recall-5801396 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172429/https://gizmodo.com/what-was-it-like-being-a-stunt-director-on-total-recall-5801396 | date = 2011-05-12 | website = [[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。电影初使预算三千万美元<ref name="LATimesDec1988" />，实际耗资据报在4800至8000万美元范围{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="AFIBio" /><ref>{{cite web | first = Aljean | last = Harmetz | title = It's Fade-Out for the Cheap Film As Hollywood's Budgets Soar | access-date = 2022-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516173931/https://www.nytimes.com/1989/12/07/movies/it-s-fade-out-for-the-cheap-film-as-hollywood-s-budgets-soar.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1989-12-07 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1989/12/07/movies/it-s-fade-out-for-the-cheap-film-as-hollywood-s-budgets-soar.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Vest" />{{rp|29,184}}<ref name="Hughes" />{{rp|77}}}}。影片几乎全在[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]][[楚鲁巴斯科制片厂|楚鲁巴斯科制片厂]]取景，43名演员与最多五百剧组人员辗转十个摄影棚的45个外景地。地球上的地铁站在[[墨西哥城地铁|墨西哥城地铁]]摄制，大量火星外景取自[[内华达州|内华达州]][[克拉克縣_(內華達州)|克拉克县]][[奥弗顿_(内华达州)|奥弗顿]][[火焰谷州立公园|火焰谷州立公园]]。{{r