=== 票房 ===
1990年6月1日，《全面回忆》在美国和加拿大2060家电影院上映，周末收入2550万位居榜首，平均每家院线12395美元，超过上映第二周的《回到未来III》（1030万美元）、第三周的《[[轰天俏娇娃|轰天俏娇娃]]》（630万美元），还以微弱优势打破《[[忍者神龟_(1990年电影)|忍者神龟]]》创下的年度电影首映周末票房纪录，位居影史新片上架三日成绩前十{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="ringer june2020" /><ref>{{cite web| title = Domestic 1990 Weekend 22 June 1–3, 1990 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W22/ | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W22/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Richard W. | last = Stevenson | title = A Real Blockbuster, Or Merely a Smash? | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/22/business/a-real-blockbuster-or-merely-a-smash.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-06-22 | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172445/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/22/business/a-real-blockbuster-or-merely-a-smash.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Pat H.| last = Broeske| title = 'Total Recall' Totally Dominates Box Office : Movies: Film starring Schwarzenegger posts one of the top 10 biggest three-day openings ever. | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1990-06-04 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-04-ca-608-story.html | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-04-ca-608-story.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。第二个周末电影收入1500万美元位居第二，比上周少四成一，落后新上映的《48小时闯天关》（1950万美元）。第三个周末本片以1020万美元排第三，落后《48小时闯天关》（1070万美元）和新上映的《迪克·特雷西》（2250万美元）。<ref>{{cite web| title = Domestic 1990 Weekend 23 June 8–10, 1990 | access-date = 2022-05-24 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W23/ | website = Box Office Mojo | archive-date = 2021-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211119042118/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W23/ | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title = Domestic 1990 Weekend 24 June 15–17, 1990 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W24/ | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172449/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/1990W24/ | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

七月中旬，《全面回忆》票房已突破一亿美元大关，跻身卖座电影行列<ref>{{cite web | first = Larry | last = Rohter | title = Hollywood Looks Beyond Mayhem For a Blockbuster | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/07/12/movies/hollywood-looks-beyond-mayhem-for-a-blockbuster.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-07-12 | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172449/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/07/12/movies/hollywood-looks-beyond-mayhem-for-a-blockbuster.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。电影持续上映16个周末，只有首周位居票房榜首，此后逐渐下跌，七月末跌出前十<ref>{{cite web | title = Total Recall | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl74941953/weekend/ | website = Box Office Mojo | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211110222331/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl74941953/weekend/ | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片北美总票房1.19亿美元，乃暑期电影票房亚军，仅次于大黑马《[[人鬼情未了|人鬼情未了]]》，在全年排行榜位居第七，落后《[[追擊赤色十月_(電影)|猎杀红色十月]]》（1.2亿美元）、《忍者神龟》（1.35亿美元）、《[[麻雀變鳳凰|麻雀變鳳凰]]》（1.78亿美元）、《[[與狼共舞|與狼共舞]]》（1.84亿美元）、《人鬼情未了》（2.18亿美元）、《[[小鬼當家|小鬼當家]]》（2.86亿美元）{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="WiredPKD" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Top 1990 Movies at the Domestic Box Office | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1990 | website = [[The_Numbers|The Numbers]] | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/domestic/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1990 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = Larry | last = Rohter | title = Love Conquers All in Hollywood Summer Season | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/09/12/movies/love-conquers-all-in-hollywood-summer-season.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-09-22 | access-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/09/12/movies/love-conquers-all-in-hollywood-summer-season.html}}</ref><ref name="NYTimesNov31990">{{cite web | first = Larry | last = Rohter | title = Top Movie Of the Year A Sleeper: It's 'Ghost' | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/11/03/movies/top-movie-of-the-year-a-sleeper-it-s-ghost.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-11-03 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/11/03/movies/top-movie-of-the-year-a-sleeper-it-s-ghost.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>}}。

美加以往国家和地区上映的票房成绩已不可考，传媒估计为1.42亿美元，全球票房总额升至2.61亿美元，位居[[1990年电影|年度票房榜第五]]，仅次于《与狼共舞》（4.24亿美元）、《漂亮女人》（4.33亿美元）、《小鬼当家》（4.77亿美元）、《人鬼情未了》（5.18亿美元）{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="WiredPKD" /><ref name="ringer june2020" /><ref name="AFIBio" /><ref>{{cite web | title = Top 1990 Movies at the Worldwide Box Office | url = https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/worldwide/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1990 | website = The Numbers | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.the-numbers.com/box-office-records/worldwide/all-movies/cumulative/released-in-1990}}</ref>}}。去除制作费、利息、待付款项，估计《全面回忆》共为制片商赚得3600万美元利润<ref>{{cite web | first = Richard W.| last = Stevenson | title = Carolco Flexes Its Muscle Overseas | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1991/06/26/business/carolco-flexes-its-muscle-overseas.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1991-06-26 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.nytimes.com/1991/06/26/business/carolco-flexes-its-muscle-overseas.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
[[File:Arnold_Schwarzenegger_1991_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]（摄于1991年）在本片突破动作英雄戏路，扮演心怀同情且具脆弱一面的人物，赢得普遍好评，但也有评论认为他的演技还不足以驾驶]]

《全面回忆》上映后反响不一，影评人普遍认可影片制作价值和施瓦辛格的演出，但批评电影过于暴力血腥<ref name="AFIBio" /><ref name="LATimesJune51990">{{cite web | first = Pat H. | last = Broeske | title = 'Recall' Totally Outdistances 'Future' in Box-Office Race : Movies: Schwarzenegger's sci-fi flick opens with $25.5 million. But it only just edges the 'Turtles' $25.3-million record. | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1990-06-05 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-05-ca-641-story.html | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-05-ca-641-story.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ScreenRantReviews">{{cite web | first = Mike | last = Jones | title = Chance The Rapper Argues Eddie Murphy Should Have Starred In Total Recall | url = https://screenrant.com/total-recall-eddie-murphy-chance-rapper-fan-casting/ | website = [[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] | date = 2021-06-23 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://screenrant.com/total-recall-eddie-murphy-chance-rapper-fan-casting/ | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[影院评分|影院评分]]观众民调显示影迷为本片打出的平均分达“A–”（最高“A+”）<ref>需在“{{lang|en|FIND CINEMASCORE}}”下面的搜索框输入电影原名“{{lang|en|Total Recall}}”，从弹出的两项选择“1990”项，页面会自动显示评分：{{Cite web | url = https://www.cinemascore.com/ | title = CinemaScore | publisher = [[影院评分|CinemaScore]] | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-date = 2018-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180102130540/https://www.cinemascore.com/ }}</ref>。

影评人对电影叙事评价趋于两极分化，有些认为影片表现高于平均水准，剧情复杂、视觉上引人入胜，将幽默与针对科幻电影的讽刺有效结合{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="ReviewVariety">{{cite web | title = Total Recall | url = https://variety.com/1989/film/reviews/total-recall-2-1200428174/ | website = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | date = 1990-01-01 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-date = 2021-10-20 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211020131156/https://variety.com/1989/film/reviews/total-recall-2-1200428174/ }}</ref><ref name="ReviewLATimes">{{cite web | first = Michael | last = Wilmington | title = Movie Review : Total Schwarzenegger : Film: Paul Verhoeven's futuristic action-thriller 'Total Recall' plunges the muscular hero in a deadly game of mind over matter. | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-01-ca-48-story.html | website = Los Angeles Times | date = 1990-06-01 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1990-06-01-ca-48-story.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ReviewNYTimes">{{cite web | first = Janet | last = Maslin | title = Review/Film; A Schwarzenegger Torn Between Lives on Earth and Mars | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/01/movies/review-film-a-schwarzenegger-torn-between-lives-on-earth-and-mars.html | website = The New York Times | date = 1990-06-01 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/01/movies/review-film-a-schwarzenegger-torn-between-lives-on-earth-and-mars.html | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ReviewRogerEbert">{{cite web | first = Roger | last = Ebert | author-link = 罗杰·埃伯特 | title = Total Recall | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/total-recall-1990 | website = RogerEbert.com | date = 1990-06-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/total-recall-1990 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2022-05-25 }}</ref>}}；也有文章批评本片幽默和浪漫不足，叙事结构不严谨<ref name="ReviewNYTimes" /><ref name="ReviewChicagoTribune2">{{cite web | first = Johanna | last = Steinmetz | title = Faulty 'Recall' | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | access-date = 2022-05-25 | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1990-06-01-9004180291-story.html | date = 1990-06-01 | website = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1990-06-01-9004180291-story.html }}</ref>。[[吉恩·西斯科尔|吉恩·西斯科尔]]与[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]认为魁德赶往火星开始的电影后半部趋于“机械”，为过火的动作与暴力放弃逻辑和艺术雄心{{refn|group="注"|见以下文献：<ref name="ReviewNYTimes" /><ref name="ReviewChicagoTribune2" /><ref name="ReviewChicagoTribune">{{cite web | first = Gene | last = Siskel | title = 'Total Recall' Starts Well | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1990-06-01-9002140540-story.html | date = 1990-06-01 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | website = Chicago Tribune | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1990-06-01-9002140540-story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ReviewWAPOKempley">{{cite web | first = Rita | last = Kempley | title = 'Total Recall' (R) | archive-date = 2020-11-29 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/totalrecallrkempley_a0a014.htm | website = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | date = 1990-06-01 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201129091115/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/totalrecallrkempley_a0a014.htm }}</ref><ref name="ReviewRollingStone">{{cite web | first = Peter | last = Travers | author-link = 彼得·崔維斯 | title = Total Recall | url = https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-reviews/total-recall-2-102852/ | website = [[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] | date = 1990-06-01 | access-date = 2022-05-25 | archive-date = 2022-05-16 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220516172444/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/movie-reviews/total-recall-2-102852/ }}</ref>}}。特拉弗斯表示，与同样由施瓦辛格主演的《[[终结者|终结者]]》相比，《全面回忆》虽是大片，但惊艳感仅昙花一现，不像《终结者》那样令人“噩梦连连”<ref name="ReviewRollingStone" />。多篇评论把瑞可公司职员艾吉马大夫在火星酒店与魁德面谈，后者首度得知一切可能只是梦境的情节评为全片最佳桥段<ref name="ReviewLATimes" /><ref name="ReviewNYTimes" /><ref name="ReviewRogerEbert" />，认可覆盖记忆和身份的确非常可怕<ref name="ReviewLATimes" /><ref name="ReviewRollingStone" />。[[乔纳森·罗森鲍姆|乔纳森·罗森鲍姆]]声称本片属《银翼杀手》开创的“反乌托邦”流派而且很有价值，不止是前辈作品的衍生<ref>{{cite web | first = Jonathan | last = Rosenbaum | title = Total Recall | url = https://chicagoreader.com/arts-culture/total-recall/ | website = Chicago Reader | access-date = 2022-05-26 | date = 1990-05-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080629021727/http://onfilm.chicagoreader.com/movies/capsules/8502_TOTAL_RECALL | archive-date = 2008-06-29 | dead-url = no}}</ref>。

